Content: anyone know the changes neded on z-nomp to facilitate asics?

Author: Captain_Jack#0015
Content: assuming its going to be  variance setting in main conf.json

Author: Alright#0419
Content: @Captain_Jack nothing in particular

Author: Alright#0419
Content: you can set the diff higher on one of the stratum ports, but it's only necessary if you want to save bandwidth

Author: Alright#0419
Content:
so in pool_configs file, you would adjust this 
```
         "4552": {
            "tls":false,
            "diff": 40,
            "varDiff": {
                "minDiff": 1,
                "maxDiff": 1000,
                "targetTime": 15,
                "retargetTime": 60,
                "variancePercent": 30
                }
            }
```
